1
00:00:01,010 --> 00:00:03,510
(Episode 92)

2
00:00:03,910 --> 00:00:05,110
Mom, please eat something.

3
00:00:05,510 --> 00:00:06,710
You need to eat so you can
take your medicine.

4
00:00:09,880 --> 00:00:12,050
What's the point of taking medicine?

5
00:00:12,580 --> 00:00:13,720
Like an idiot,

6
00:00:14,790 --> 00:00:16,890
I was so clueless.

7
00:00:18,490 --> 00:00:21,290
I always thought that
even if other husbands cheated,

8
00:00:22,190 --> 00:00:24,130
my husband never would.

9
00:00:25,460 --> 00:00:27,270
I took so much pride in that.

10
00:00:28,670 --> 00:00:29,730
I thought I was...

11
00:00:30,940 --> 00:00:32,670
the only woman in his world.

12
00:00:35,710 --> 00:00:37,640
Turns out it was right under my nose
the whole time...

13
00:00:38,980 --> 00:00:40,410
I couldn't tell you before...

14
00:00:41,510 --> 00:00:43,050
because I was afraid
you'd be this torn up.

15
00:00:44,650 --> 00:00:46,990
Mom, you're amazing just as you are.

16
00:00:47,820 --> 00:00:50,960
Dad is just under Chae Hwa Young's spell,
and she's using him,

17
00:00:51,290 --> 00:00:52,520
which he's completely oblivious about.

18
00:00:58,360 --> 00:00:59,400
I got you some herbal medicine.

19
00:01:00,100 --> 00:01:01,170
Please take it after you eat.

20
00:01:04,140 --> 00:01:05,140
Jun Ho.

21
00:01:05,970 --> 00:01:08,910
Were you unaware of this too?

22
00:01:09,570 --> 00:01:11,410
I never thought Dad was capable of this.

23
00:01:12,080 --> 00:01:13,080
Alright.

24
00:01:14,150 --> 00:01:15,350
Anyway.

25
00:01:17,280 --> 00:01:18,620
I'm sorry about all this.

26
00:01:20,520 --> 00:01:21,720
Because of your parents,

27
00:01:23,990 --> 00:01:26,160
you have to call off your wedding.

28
00:01:27,030 --> 00:01:28,030
No, Mother.

29
00:01:29,090 --> 00:01:30,930
We're going ahead
with the wedding as planned.

30
00:01:33,900 --> 00:01:34,900
What?

31
00:01:35,730 --> 00:01:39,040
You're just going to get married anyway?

32
00:01:40,000 --> 00:01:41,010
Yes.

33
00:01:41,370 --> 00:01:45,080
- Jun Ho!
- Jun Ho, I can't believe you.

34
00:01:46,680 --> 00:01:50,280
Are you only thinking of yourself
in a situation like this?

35
00:01:50,520 --> 00:01:54,890
I've worked to the bone my whole life
to be a son you could be proud of.

36
00:01:55,490 --> 00:01:58,320
Have I ever once gone against
your wishes, Mother?

37
00:01:59,120 --> 00:02:00,460
That may be,

38
00:02:00,530 --> 00:02:05,330
but that's different
from insisting on this wedding now.

39
00:02:05,400 --> 00:02:07,100
No matter how much you object,

40
00:02:08,670 --> 00:02:09,800
I'm going through with this marriage.

41
00:02:11,940 --> 00:02:15,010
- Jun Ho, this isn't right.
- Stay out of this, Baek Ho.

42
00:02:15,470 --> 00:02:18,110
- Why are you meddling in my wedding?
- Don't you care about Mom?

43
00:02:18,740 --> 00:02:21,050
How can Mom become in-laws
with Dad's mistress?

44
00:02:21,110 --> 00:02:22,350
That's between our parents.

45
00:02:23,210 --> 00:02:25,720
It's not like I'm marrying our parents.

46
00:02:26,550 --> 00:02:29,420
I'm marrying Director Ma Seo Rin.

47
00:02:57,320 --> 00:02:58,320
Nam Bong.

48
00:02:59,020 --> 00:03:02,090
Whatever it takes, we have to make sure
Jun Ho and Seo Rin get married.

49
00:03:02,590 --> 00:03:05,760
That's the only way
Chairman Ma won't find out about us.

50
00:03:06,390 --> 00:03:08,960
If he does, I'll be thrown out,
and I'll lose everything.

51
00:03:09,830 --> 00:03:11,660
Nam Bong, is that what you want for me?

52
00:03:12,260 --> 00:03:16,800
Your way of loving me can't be
to watch me crash and burn, can it?

53
00:03:19,940 --> 00:03:21,370
I want us to become in-laws...

54
00:03:21,440 --> 00:03:24,610
so we can
still see each other fondly, Nam Bong.

55
00:03:25,540 --> 00:03:29,110
If you love me, please,
just grant me this one wish.

56
00:03:29,810 --> 00:03:31,880
We can start over.

57
00:03:32,720 --> 00:03:34,150
I love you, Nam Bong.

58
00:03:57,940 --> 00:03:59,280
I'm sorry, Young Ja.

59
00:03:59,640 --> 00:04:02,010
I deserve to die for what I've done.

60
00:04:06,120 --> 00:04:07,420
I told you to leave.
Why did you come back?

61
00:04:08,350 --> 00:04:10,960
- Who said you could come back?
- Please, don't be like this.

62
00:04:12,990 --> 00:04:17,000
Even a cornered rat needs an escape route.

63
00:04:20,370 --> 00:04:22,570
Get out! I can't stand the sight of you.

64
00:04:22,700 --> 00:04:24,100
Get out of my face!

65
00:04:24,700 --> 00:04:28,010
Go on, live your fabulous life
in technicolor with that tramp.

66
00:04:33,180 --> 00:04:35,050
- Please, stop.
- How did you...

67
00:04:35,250 --> 00:04:38,120
live this long with someone
as boring as me?

68
00:04:40,080 --> 00:04:43,220
You must've just gone through the motions
like some empty shell.

69
00:04:43,690 --> 00:04:46,790
And I never knew.
What a complete and utter fool I am!

70
00:04:47,730 --> 00:04:50,530
I know you've been nothing but good to me.

71
00:04:51,060 --> 00:04:54,300
- If I didn't, I wouldn't even be human.
- Human?

72
00:04:54,900 --> 00:04:56,030
You call yourself human?

73
00:04:56,530 --> 00:04:59,000
You might want to be, but you're not.

74
00:05:00,140 --> 00:05:03,040
You and that tramp,
Chae Hwa Young, are garbage.

75
00:05:03,840 --> 00:05:07,550
Not even worth recycling.
Just a pile of useless, disgusting filth!

76
00:05:07,750 --> 00:05:11,650
Fine. Take it all out on me
until you feel better.

77
00:05:12,020 --> 00:05:14,590
And whatever it is you want from me,

78
00:05:15,620 --> 00:05:16,620
I'll do it.

79
00:05:18,860 --> 00:05:19,960
Where do you think you're going?

80
00:05:20,660 --> 00:05:22,030
I'm not finished with you yet!

81
00:05:25,900 --> 00:05:27,200
Then what am I supposed to do?

82
00:05:27,530 --> 00:05:28,600
What are you supposed to do?

83
00:05:30,700 --> 00:05:33,470
You stab a knife in my heart
and then ask what you're supposed to do?

84
00:05:34,770 --> 00:05:36,670
The 35 years with you...

85
00:05:38,040 --> 00:05:39,510
You turned all those long years...

86
00:05:40,710 --> 00:05:42,950
into nothing,

87
00:05:42,950 --> 00:05:44,380
and you ask what you're supposed to do?

88
00:05:44,680 --> 00:05:45,920
I already said I was sorry.

89
00:05:46,420 --> 00:05:48,590
I'm sorry! I said I'm sorry!

90
00:06:02,030 --> 00:06:04,440
How is Lawyer Han doing?

91
00:06:04,800 --> 00:06:05,800
She's not doing well.

92
00:06:06,140 --> 00:06:08,810
- It was a huge shock.
- Under these circumstances,

93
00:06:09,710 --> 00:06:11,040
are you sure we can still have a wedding?

94
00:06:11,710 --> 00:06:14,510
Lawyer Han would be deeply hurt.

95
00:06:14,610 --> 00:06:16,280
This won't affect our marriage.

96
00:06:17,010 --> 00:06:18,480
I said it wouldn't matter.

97
00:06:18,850 --> 00:06:19,850
You know,

98
00:06:20,180 --> 00:06:23,550
it seems like you're the one
who doesn't treat your family like family.

99
00:06:24,560 --> 00:06:27,660
Don't tell me you're starting to feel
some motherly affection for CEO Chae.

100
00:06:29,430 --> 00:06:31,400
That is a deeply insulting thing
for you to say.

101
00:06:32,130 --> 00:06:33,130
Please watch what you say.

102
00:06:35,570 --> 00:06:37,270
Just because I love you, Jang Mi,

103
00:06:37,670 --> 00:06:39,740
it doesn't mean I have any intention
of abandoning my family.

104
00:06:40,200 --> 00:06:42,610
The more they oppose our marriage,
the harder I'll work to be good to them.

105
00:06:43,540 --> 00:06:44,540
And...

106
00:06:45,180 --> 00:06:46,640
CEO Chae is nothing...

107
00:06:47,480 --> 00:06:48,680
compared to my parents.

108
00:07:02,130 --> 00:07:03,900
What's wrong, Baek Ho?

109
00:07:03,900 --> 00:07:04,900
Are you dizzy?

110
00:07:05,300 --> 00:07:07,570
No. I just didn't
get any sleep last night.

111
00:07:08,830 --> 00:07:11,100
It's probably because you haven't eaten
since yesterday.

112
00:07:11,100 --> 00:07:12,200
You skipped lunch, too.

113
00:07:12,870 --> 00:07:15,540
Let's get you to the infirmary.
I'll take you.

114
00:07:16,640 --> 00:07:17,640
No, I'm okay...

115
00:07:20,480 --> 00:07:22,350
Right, that's how it must've been.

116
00:07:23,450 --> 00:07:26,850
Because of his mom,
Baek Ho hasn't been able to sleep or eat.

117
00:07:27,750 --> 00:07:29,090
And he's already having such a hard time.

118
00:07:30,420 --> 00:07:31,690
I feel so bad for you, Baek Ho.

119
00:07:41,400 --> 00:07:42,400
So, how did it go?

120
00:07:42,900 --> 00:07:44,270
Did you get the gift ready?

121
00:07:45,100 --> 00:07:46,900
- Yes.
- Let's go.

122
00:07:47,740 --> 00:07:49,510
Professor Kang may have
laid some groundwork,

123
00:07:50,070 --> 00:07:52,710
but I doubt that was enough
to make Han Young Ja change her mind.

124
00:07:53,880 --> 00:07:57,110
- Still, we have to do everything we can.
- I know.

125
00:07:58,020 --> 00:07:59,950
You should have stopped
when I told you to.

126
00:08:00,690 --> 00:08:01,750
So what are you going to do now?

127
00:08:02,690 --> 00:08:04,460
Did you like Kang Nam Bong that much?

128
00:08:04,460 --> 00:08:07,190
Lee Kang Hyuk! Why make it worse?

129
00:08:07,730 --> 00:08:11,100
I haven't slept a wink,
and I'm losing my mind as it is.

130
00:08:11,160 --> 00:08:12,360
That's my point.

131
00:08:13,430 --> 00:08:15,330
Look, I'm only saying this
because I'm upset too.

132
00:08:19,070 --> 00:08:20,140
You have got to be kidding me.

133
00:08:26,840 --> 00:08:28,210
Are you here to rub salt in the wound?

134
00:08:29,110 --> 00:08:30,850
As if I'm just dying for some ribs?

135
00:08:31,420 --> 00:08:33,750
- Mrs. Han...
- Don't you "Mrs. Han" me!

136
00:08:35,250 --> 00:08:37,150
Have you no shame
in front of your own daughter?

137
00:08:37,920 --> 00:08:39,490
How dare you show your face...

138
00:08:40,320 --> 00:08:42,530
after having an affair
with your daughter's future father-in-law?

139
00:08:50,000 --> 00:08:51,270
What do you think you're doing?

140
00:08:51,340 --> 00:08:53,540
I won't ask you to forgive me.

141
00:08:55,170 --> 00:08:56,170
However,

142
00:08:56,640 --> 00:09:00,080
I want to clear up your misunderstanding.

143
00:09:00,080 --> 00:09:01,450
Please, just hear me out.

144
00:09:01,450 --> 00:09:04,180
Then why are you kneeling?

145
00:09:05,350 --> 00:09:07,450
Are you rubbing it in
to make me uncomfortable?

146
00:09:07,890 --> 00:09:08,890
The truth is,

147
00:09:09,590 --> 00:09:13,060
I admit I met Professor Kang through work
and had a moment of weakness.

148
00:09:13,990 --> 00:09:16,890
But it's not the kind of relationship
you're imagining, Lawyer Han.

149
00:09:17,530 --> 00:09:20,130
And we never crossed that line.

150
00:09:20,130 --> 00:09:21,570
I saw you with my own two eyes,

151
00:09:22,030 --> 00:09:23,570
and you're telling me
you didn't cross the line?

152
00:09:24,740 --> 00:09:27,070
- The nerve.
- That was because...

153
00:09:28,970 --> 00:09:31,640
Professor Kang was so dead set
against this wedding,

154
00:09:32,580 --> 00:09:35,880
so I told a small lie to calm him down.
That's all, I swear.

155
00:09:37,080 --> 00:09:41,050
My daughter's happiness
is my number one priority.

156
00:09:41,520 --> 00:09:44,720
What parent would ever want to see
their own child unhappy?

157
00:09:44,790 --> 00:09:46,890
If you really cared that much
about your child,

158
00:09:47,860 --> 00:09:50,190
you wouldn't be flirting with the father
of the one she loves.

159
00:09:50,190 --> 00:09:51,300
I didn't know.

160
00:09:52,160 --> 00:09:54,130
I didn't know my daughter
was in love with Jun Ho.

161
00:09:56,030 --> 00:09:59,900
So, you're saying you two were already
involved before that?

162
00:10:00,340 --> 00:10:02,210
You had me completely fooled,

163
00:10:02,540 --> 00:10:05,710
and you still want our kids to marry?
And what?

164
00:10:06,040 --> 00:10:08,510
- Get hanboks fitted?
- Mrs. Han.

165
00:10:15,050 --> 00:10:17,050
I told you to stop calling me "Mrs. Han"!

166
00:10:18,360 --> 00:10:20,220
There is no way
our children are getting married!

167
00:10:20,390 --> 00:10:22,630
Jun Ho says it has to be
my daughter or no one.

168
00:10:23,790 --> 00:10:26,930
For Jun Ho's sake,
please, just give in. Okay?

169
00:10:27,500 --> 00:10:29,700
Don't think about anything else.

170
00:10:30,270 --> 00:10:32,070
Just focus on Jun Ho's future.

171
00:10:32,770 --> 00:10:34,240
He's the son you love.

172
00:10:34,240 --> 00:10:35,840
I've heard enough of your nonsense.

173
00:10:36,740 --> 00:10:37,740
Get out, now.

174
00:10:38,410 --> 00:10:39,410
And...

175
00:10:40,140 --> 00:10:43,850
don't you ever show that filthy face
of yours to me again.

176
00:10:44,550 --> 00:10:45,720
You make me sick.

177
00:11:08,140 --> 00:11:09,140
What's all this?

178
00:11:09,410 --> 00:11:11,580
Director Ma said...

179
00:11:11,810 --> 00:11:14,780
the subcontractor brought them to thank us
for helping them out.

180
00:11:15,750 --> 00:11:18,380
Was that instant porridge
in the break room?

181
00:11:18,880 --> 00:11:20,250
I heard they left some there, too.

182
00:11:20,790 --> 00:11:23,350
- I'm going to have some of that later.
- Right.

183
00:11:23,690 --> 00:11:25,990
Baek Ho, want to get some porridge
with me?

184
00:11:26,390 --> 00:11:30,030
- That and an energy drink will help.
- I'll go later.

185
00:11:34,570 --> 00:11:35,730
By the way, Baek Ho.

186
00:11:36,100 --> 00:11:38,100
Touching your ear like that
must be a habit of yours.

187
00:11:38,540 --> 00:11:39,640
You do it quite often.

188
00:11:40,840 --> 00:11:43,670
Team Leader Jin.
Since you're up, heat one up for me.

189
00:11:43,670 --> 00:11:44,780
What?

190
00:11:45,280 --> 00:11:48,080
But we're not supposed to eat
in the office.

191
00:11:48,150 --> 00:11:50,650
Says who? We can eat here if we want.

192
00:11:50,710 --> 00:11:52,250
Hurry up. I'm hungry.

193
00:11:53,550 --> 00:11:54,550
Okay, fine.

194
00:11:55,050 --> 00:11:58,190
I'll heat yours up too, Baek Ho,
so make sure you eat it.

195
00:11:59,320 --> 00:12:00,320
No, I...

196
00:12:06,560 --> 00:12:08,370
Please, stop being so stubborn...

197
00:12:08,830 --> 00:12:11,440
and just eat something
to get your strength back, Baek Ho.

198
00:12:19,740 --> 00:12:20,740
What do I do?

199
00:12:21,250 --> 00:12:23,050
What if the wedding really gets called off
because of this?

200
00:12:23,450 --> 00:12:24,880
What a headache.

201
00:12:36,690 --> 00:12:39,860
Hey, Seo Rin, what's wrong? Are you hurt?

202
00:12:40,230 --> 00:12:42,530
What in the... Jun Ho...

203
00:12:42,900 --> 00:12:46,070
- I mean, General Manager Kang.
- What's going on?

204
00:12:46,570 --> 00:12:48,110
Is Seo Rin hurt?

205
00:12:48,370 --> 00:12:49,410
She's not hurt.

206
00:12:50,040 --> 00:12:51,480
She said her leg was a bit swollen.

207
00:12:52,580 --> 00:12:55,180
Grandfather, my leg hurts.

208
00:12:55,180 --> 00:12:56,380
This girl...

209
00:12:56,780 --> 00:12:59,280
Why make General Manager Kang
struggle over nothing?

210
00:12:59,280 --> 00:13:00,450
Get down, Seo Rin.

211
00:13:00,650 --> 00:13:01,790
Seriously, Mom.

212
00:13:02,090 --> 00:13:04,260
We're getting married.
What's the big deal?

213
00:13:04,790 --> 00:13:07,160
Look at them,
so brazen with their flirting.

214
00:13:08,030 --> 00:13:09,890
Grandfather, just bear with us
a little longer.

215
00:13:09,990 --> 00:13:12,830
General Manager Kang is getting tired.
Hurry and get down now.

216
00:13:14,000 --> 00:13:15,170
- Jun Ho.
- Yes.

217
00:13:15,170 --> 00:13:17,000
- Put me down over there.
- Okay.

218
00:13:22,370 --> 00:13:24,740
Good grief, you rascal.

219
00:13:25,410 --> 00:13:28,850
- You should stay for dinner. All right?
- Okay.

220
00:13:28,910 --> 00:13:29,910
I'm just going to go change.

221
00:13:31,350 --> 00:13:34,350
That's right, General Manager Kang.
You must be tired after carrying Seo Rin.

222
00:13:35,090 --> 00:13:36,550
Oh my, look at you, all sweaty.

223
00:13:37,120 --> 00:13:39,190
Mrs. Yang, please bring a towel, quickly.

224
00:13:39,460 --> 00:13:41,830
- No, I'm fine, thank you.
- Jun Ho.

225
00:13:42,430 --> 00:13:43,460
I need some water.

226
00:13:43,790 --> 00:13:44,830
Stop it, Ma Seo Rin.

227
00:13:45,530 --> 00:13:47,230
You're being so rude
to General Manager Kang.

228
00:13:49,100 --> 00:13:51,170
This is how we show our affection.

229
00:13:51,470 --> 00:13:53,300
Haven't you and Dad ever done
things like this?

230
00:13:54,070 --> 00:13:56,410
So that's why you and Professor Kang...

231
00:13:56,470 --> 00:13:58,210
That's enough, Ma Seo Rin.

232
00:13:59,180 --> 00:14:00,840
I guess I had too much to drink.

233
00:14:01,380 --> 00:14:03,480
I'm feeling a little dizzy.

234
00:14:04,220 --> 00:14:05,220
Excuse me,

235
00:14:06,220 --> 00:14:07,790
do you have any lemons in the kitchen?

236
00:14:07,890 --> 00:14:10,220
Yes, I believe we do.

237
00:14:11,390 --> 00:14:13,920
Have some lemon water.
It'll help you feel better.

238
00:14:14,960 --> 00:14:15,960
It's fine, General Manager Kang.

239
00:14:16,630 --> 00:14:19,130
Have a seat. I'll take care of Seo Rin.

240
00:14:19,200 --> 00:14:22,630
Jun Ho. Please take me to my room.

241
00:14:23,000 --> 00:14:24,800
I think I need to go lie down.

242
00:14:25,700 --> 00:14:27,140
On second thought.

243
00:14:27,870 --> 00:14:30,570
But then you'd have to carry me
upstairs again, Jun Ho.

244
00:14:31,540 --> 00:14:33,680
That would be too much for you,
wouldn't it?

245
00:14:37,050 --> 00:14:39,750
I thought she was clueless,
but she's a sly little fox.

246
00:14:40,420 --> 00:14:42,820
That little wench has my Jun Ho
completely wrapped around her finger.

247
00:14:43,190 --> 00:14:46,560
No, that would be too hard for you.
Never mind.

248
00:14:48,830 --> 00:14:51,600
I'm still dizzy. I need your help.

249
00:14:51,960 --> 00:14:54,100
- Here, take my hand.
- I'm so dizzy.

250
00:14:55,230 --> 00:14:58,200
- Jun Ho, grab the shopping bag.
- Okay.

251
00:15:05,340 --> 00:15:08,910
Oh Jang Mi. I will make you pay for this.

252
00:15:10,080 --> 00:15:12,320
You're burning up inside,
aren't you, Chae Hwa Young?

253
00:15:12,950 --> 00:15:14,050
Just you wait.

254
00:15:14,050 --> 00:15:18,020
After I marry Jun Ho,
I'm going to tear your heart to pieces.

255
00:15:19,690 --> 00:15:20,760
Shall we head up?

256
00:15:27,260 --> 00:15:28,270
Are you okay?

257
00:15:28,630 --> 00:15:29,630
Yes.

258
00:15:33,700 --> 00:15:35,870
I'm fine. You should get going.

259
00:15:36,170 --> 00:15:37,570
But you asked me to take you to your room.

260
00:15:38,040 --> 00:15:41,680
Please, just follow my lead.

261
00:15:43,010 --> 00:15:45,250
All right. I'll back off for today.

262
00:15:45,580 --> 00:15:47,180
Thanks for playing along today.

263
00:15:47,650 --> 00:15:49,650
I'm fine now, so you should get going.

264
00:16:03,630 --> 00:16:05,500
I don't have to feel guilty about Jun Ho.

265
00:16:06,540 --> 00:16:08,640
The only person in my life
I need to feel sorry for,

266
00:16:09,210 --> 00:16:10,570
the one I need forgiveness from,

267
00:16:11,340 --> 00:16:12,580
is Baek Ho.

268
00:16:21,420 --> 00:16:22,890
She said she had a headache.

269
00:16:23,620 --> 00:16:24,960
I wonder if she's all right.

270
00:16:44,240 --> 00:16:46,740
No! Give me back my baby!

271
00:16:46,810 --> 00:16:49,350
- No!
- Jung Suk Hee, get this straight.

272
00:16:50,110 --> 00:16:52,120
From now on, this baby is mine.

273
00:16:52,380 --> 00:16:54,280
I said she's my baby now!

274
00:16:55,250 --> 00:16:56,450
No, that's my baby.

275
00:16:58,490 --> 00:16:59,860
Please give her back.

276
00:17:02,990 --> 00:17:06,160
Ms. Chae Hwa Young.
I'll do anything you want.

277
00:17:06,900 --> 00:17:08,370
Just please, not my babies.

278
00:17:09,330 --> 00:17:11,000
Please give my babies back.

279
00:17:11,470 --> 00:17:13,740
Please don't do this!

280
00:17:34,830 --> 00:17:36,830
Father, take a look at this.

281
00:17:37,330 --> 00:17:39,000
There's an article about...

282
00:17:39,360 --> 00:17:42,700
- Seo Rin and Kang Jun Ho's wedding.
- So there is.

283
00:17:44,300 --> 00:17:46,040
(Exclusive: Chairman Ma's granddaughter,
Ma Seo Rin,)

284
00:17:46,100 --> 00:17:47,810
(to marry Dream Hotel's General Manager
Kang Jun Ho)

285
00:17:51,280 --> 00:17:53,410
Looks like your wish came true, Seo Rin.

286
00:17:54,380 --> 00:17:56,510
After all your talk about
how much you liked General Manager Kang,

287
00:17:56,850 --> 00:18:00,780
and now there's no backing out.
You're finally getting married to him.

288
00:18:01,490 --> 00:18:02,650
Congratulations, Seo Rin.

289
00:18:04,120 --> 00:18:06,390
Thanks, Mom. Thank you, Grandfather.

290
00:18:07,020 --> 00:18:08,630
Of course.

291
00:18:09,490 --> 00:18:10,560
Hwa Young.

292
00:18:11,260 --> 00:18:13,500
About the formal family meeting...

293
00:18:14,230 --> 00:18:16,530
What if we invite them over
to our home for dinner?

294
00:18:16,900 --> 00:18:18,270
Invite them here?

295
00:18:18,340 --> 00:18:20,200
Well, it's not like we're strangers.

296
00:18:20,670 --> 00:18:24,170
And I'm sure his family will be curious
to see the house where he'll be living.

297
00:18:24,310 --> 00:18:25,440
We can give them a tour.

298
00:18:25,810 --> 00:18:28,910
Yes. I'll discuss it with them, Father.

299
00:18:32,150 --> 00:18:33,150
Mother.

300
00:18:33,650 --> 00:18:35,520
I want you to come
to Chairman Ma's house this weekend...

301
00:18:35,520 --> 00:18:37,150
for the formal family meeting.

302
00:18:39,260 --> 00:18:41,790
- What?
- I understand why you're against this.

303
00:18:42,460 --> 00:18:45,100
- But?
- But please try to see my point of view.

304
00:18:46,460 --> 00:18:48,230
I'm truly in love with Ma Seo Rin.

305
00:18:50,130 --> 00:18:51,940
So please, you have to be there.

306
00:18:53,440 --> 00:18:54,510
I'm begging you.

307
00:18:57,810 --> 00:18:58,810
Jun Ho.

308
00:19:05,950 --> 00:19:06,950
Kang Jun Ho.

309
00:19:08,550 --> 00:19:10,650
Are you that anxious
to get my blessing for this marriage?

310
00:19:11,860 --> 00:19:15,490
You're a mess
because you're afraid I'll stop you.

311
00:19:18,760 --> 00:19:20,900
Don't you care at all that
you're breaking my heart...

312
00:19:22,530 --> 00:19:24,770
when I raised
and cared for you all this time?

313
00:19:26,400 --> 00:19:28,170
How could you be so inconsiderate?

314
00:19:28,710 --> 00:19:29,710
I just can't believe it.

315
00:19:41,420 --> 00:19:42,420
All right, fine.

316
00:19:43,750 --> 00:19:45,290
If that's how you want to play it.

317
00:19:46,990 --> 00:19:47,990
Fine.

318
00:19:50,530 --> 00:19:51,830
Let's have this family meeting.

319
00:19:54,700 --> 00:19:55,970
Thank you, Mom.

320
00:20:17,420 --> 00:20:18,420
Listen up.

321
00:20:19,120 --> 00:20:20,290
The formal family meeting...

322
00:20:21,160 --> 00:20:23,790
is this weekend at Chairman Ma's.
You'd better be there.

323
00:20:24,060 --> 00:20:25,130
What's going on?

324
00:20:25,430 --> 00:20:27,460
I thought you were against
Jun Ho's marriage.

325
00:20:28,530 --> 00:20:30,170
What parent can win
against their own child?

326
00:20:34,200 --> 00:20:36,270
I'm not going.

327
00:20:37,340 --> 00:20:38,480
You go by yourself.

328
00:20:39,280 --> 00:20:43,850
Tell them I have a seminar out of town
that I absolutely can't miss.

329
00:20:45,350 --> 00:20:46,480
You know how I am.

330
00:20:47,120 --> 00:20:49,390
- I can't go to something like that.
- You're not coming?

331
00:20:49,990 --> 00:20:53,460
Fine. Go ahead and have Jun Ho resent you
for the rest of your life.

332
00:20:53,920 --> 00:20:56,390
And it'll be a huge insult to Chairman Ma.

333
00:20:57,060 --> 00:20:58,630
Go ahead and do whatever you want.

334
00:21:05,400 --> 00:21:07,170
Seriously...

335
00:21:09,310 --> 00:21:10,870
(Ditebupin)

336
00:21:12,240 --> 00:21:14,680
They increased the dosage
of my blood pressure medicine?

337
00:21:15,050 --> 00:21:18,220
Yes, they increased it
based on your last test results.

338
00:21:18,550 --> 00:21:21,390
- All right. Good work. You can go home.
- Yes, sir.

339
00:21:26,990 --> 00:21:29,430
Is it safe to increase the dosage?

340
00:21:29,790 --> 00:21:31,800
I'm sure Dr. Kim knew what he was doing.

341
00:21:32,360 --> 00:21:35,000
Wake me up when Seo Rin gets here.
I'm going to get some rest.

342
00:21:35,070 --> 00:21:37,370
Okay. You should get some rest.

343
00:21:49,010 --> 00:21:52,580
Secretary Kim got a new, higher-dose
blood pressure medication today.

344
00:21:52,920 --> 00:21:54,220
Is this the one you specifically prepared?

345
00:21:54,320 --> 00:21:58,190
Yes. Long-term use of this
will cause his blood pressure to spike,

346
00:21:58,420 --> 00:22:00,290
and it's guaranteed
to cause facial swelling.

347
00:22:00,460 --> 00:22:02,090
Facial swelling?

348
00:22:03,230 --> 00:22:04,330
Perfect.

349
00:22:04,960 --> 00:22:08,600
Everyone will just think
the old man is gaining healthy weight.

350
00:22:22,350 --> 00:22:23,750
(Ditebupin)

351
00:22:24,920 --> 00:22:26,020
(Ditebupin)

352
00:22:31,620 --> 00:22:33,390
(Ditebupin)

353
00:22:36,690 --> 00:22:38,660
(Ditebupin)

354
00:22:46,870 --> 00:22:48,470
Food for the formal family meeting?

355
00:22:48,670 --> 00:22:51,710
Our housekeeper will take care
of the basics...

356
00:22:53,310 --> 00:22:57,950
But I also wanted to see you
while I was at it, Tae Pyung.

357
00:22:59,650 --> 00:23:02,790
Plus, I have to look out for
the Chairman's health.

358
00:23:04,050 --> 00:23:07,890
- Okay.
- Suk Hee makes great side dishes.

359
00:23:07,990 --> 00:23:10,530
The side dishes Suk Hee makes
are delicious.

360
00:23:11,260 --> 00:23:13,730
But twisted donut lady,

361
00:23:14,130 --> 00:23:16,700
stop trying to twist yourself
around Tae Pyung.

362
00:23:17,330 --> 00:23:21,000
- It's pathetic.
- I'm not twisting anything.

363
00:23:21,640 --> 00:23:24,010
All right, I'll have it delivered for you.

364
00:23:24,910 --> 00:23:26,540
Thank you, Tae Pyung.

365
00:23:30,410 --> 00:23:31,450
Take care.

366
00:23:35,690 --> 00:23:36,950
A formal family meeting...

367
00:23:37,990 --> 00:23:40,860
It looks like Jang Mi is marrying
Kang Jun Ho after all.

368
00:23:42,260 --> 00:23:44,390
What am I going to do about Baek Ho?

369
00:23:47,460 --> 00:23:50,100
By the way, Mom,
when did you become so chatty?

370
00:23:50,700 --> 00:23:51,870
You're speaking clearly, too.

371
00:23:55,370 --> 00:23:58,310
Suk Hee has been
having a lot of dreams lately.

372
00:23:59,410 --> 00:24:01,610
My head keeps hurting.

373
00:24:02,510 --> 00:24:03,750
Could you be...

374
00:24:04,780 --> 00:24:06,880
getting your memories back?

375
00:24:26,070 --> 00:24:30,010
Jun Ho.
Please take good care of our Seo Rin.

376
00:24:30,540 --> 00:24:31,610
Yes, Chairman.

377
00:24:31,980 --> 00:24:34,110
Thank you for giving me your blessing
to marry Seo Rin.

378
00:24:41,820 --> 00:24:43,720
Mrs. Han, before we eat,

379
00:24:43,720 --> 00:24:46,690
would you like a tour of the house
General Manager Kang will be living in?

380
00:24:46,790 --> 00:24:47,790
That won't be necessary.

381
00:24:48,530 --> 00:24:50,660
I'm sure you've outdone yourself.
There's no need to look.

382
00:24:52,730 --> 00:24:54,660
Shall we get started with dinner, then?

383
00:25:05,110 --> 00:25:08,980
I ordered some special side dishes
for the occasion.

384
00:25:09,750 --> 00:25:11,180
You brought the sweet rice punch,
didn't you?

385
00:25:11,580 --> 00:25:12,580
Yes.

386
00:25:15,850 --> 00:25:17,990
Hello, Chairman.

387
00:25:17,990 --> 00:25:18,990
Hey.

388
00:25:25,230 --> 00:25:26,230
Oh Tae Pyung.

389
00:25:27,130 --> 00:25:29,100
I haven't seen you since we were
at the police station.

390
00:25:30,130 --> 00:25:31,570
The police station?

391
00:25:33,770 --> 00:25:36,740
Oh Tae Pyung wasn't the one there
for causing a car accident.

392
00:25:37,570 --> 00:25:41,680
It was this man who caused a car accident,
and that's where we met him.

393
00:25:43,650 --> 00:25:46,150
You remember it too, don't you, Chairman?

394
00:25:46,880 --> 00:25:49,450
The person who died in the car accident
this man caused...

395
00:25:50,350 --> 00:25:53,720
was Oh Tae Pyung's father, Oh Bok Gil.

396
00:25:55,390 --> 00:25:57,060
Isn't that right, dear?

397
00:26:00,060 --> 00:26:02,030
I'll just drop off the food
and be on my way.

398
00:26:15,280 --> 00:26:18,150
Some certified mail came
from the court for you, ma'am.

399
00:26:18,210 --> 00:26:19,680
I signed for it.

400
00:26:20,820 --> 00:26:23,750
What could this be?
Certified mail from the court?

401
00:26:24,020 --> 00:26:25,020
Go ahead and open it.

402
00:26:31,930 --> 00:26:33,830
What could this be?

403
00:26:39,800 --> 00:26:41,440
They're having
the formal family meeting today?

404
00:26:50,250 --> 00:26:52,680
(Hangang District Court)

405
00:26:58,690 --> 00:26:59,690
I think...

406
00:27:00,760 --> 00:27:02,830
you should be the one
to see this, Chairman.

407
00:27:03,990 --> 00:27:05,500
What are you doing?

408
00:27:05,560 --> 00:27:07,700
What is it? What's going on?

409
00:27:08,000 --> 00:27:10,430
Why don't you see for yourself, Chairman?

410
00:27:10,500 --> 00:27:12,770
What do you think you're doing?
That mail is for me.

411
00:27:12,770 --> 00:27:13,840
Give it here.

412
00:27:15,040 --> 00:27:16,440
Mother, what are you doing?

413
00:27:16,440 --> 00:27:18,840
- Give that to CEO Chae right now.
- No.

414
00:27:19,710 --> 00:27:23,010
This lawsuit concerns me as well,

415
00:27:23,480 --> 00:27:26,980
so it's only right that
we all see it together,

416
00:27:27,450 --> 00:27:28,490
right here and now.

417
00:27:41,800 --> 00:27:43,070
(Complaint)

418
00:27:43,130 --> 00:27:44,300
(Plaintiff: Han Young Ja,
Defendant: Chae Hwa Young)

419
00:27:44,370 --> 00:27:45,600
(Relief Sought)

420
00:27:45,670 --> 00:27:46,870
(Grounds for Claim)

421
00:27:47,070 --> 00:27:49,470
What is all this?

422
00:27:49,540 --> 00:27:53,140
Oh, my. It's a lawsuit
for emotional damages.

423
00:27:53,140 --> 00:27:54,340
Goodness.

424
00:27:54,540 --> 00:27:56,410
This was bound to happen.

425
00:27:57,050 --> 00:27:58,450
This is...

426
00:27:58,980 --> 00:28:01,180
A lawsuit for damages?

427
00:28:01,680 --> 00:28:02,920
What is the meaning of all this?

428
00:28:03,320 --> 00:28:06,460
That's just a misunderstanding
on her part, Father.

429
00:28:06,560 --> 00:28:08,560
It's no misunderstanding, Chairman.

430
00:28:10,230 --> 00:28:13,730
CEO Chae Hwa Young
is having an affair with my husband.

431
00:28:54,570 --> 00:28:56,170
(The First Man)

432
00:28:56,510 --> 00:28:58,110
What do you think you're doing?

433
00:28:58,270 --> 00:29:00,780
I will never allow this marriage.

434
00:29:01,040 --> 00:29:02,950
I have to use this to find Seo Rin.

435
00:29:03,210 --> 00:29:05,980
Are you two in love?

436
00:29:05,980 --> 00:29:07,180
- Yes, we are.
- No, we're not.

437
00:29:07,520 --> 00:29:09,950
He's been obsessively pursuing me.

438
00:29:10,090 --> 00:29:11,690
You stalker!

439
00:29:12,520 --> 00:29:13,520
Father.

440
00:29:14,120 --> 00:29:15,490
Where am I?

441
00:29:15,630 --> 00:29:18,290
And why was I lying here all alone?

442
00:29:23,070 --> 00:29:25,070
(Subtitles are provided by KOCOWA.)
